{"tid":2034504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[東網] 港版國安法：7名市民到中聯辦請願 促立法設追溯期","createTime":"2020-05-25T09:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:29:28.000Z","uid":166360,"like":15,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4796c393fb32b858d9745938b0b277ddc71fe74b","tid":2034504,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"[東網] 港版國安法：7名市民到中聯辦請願 促立法設追溯期<br />\n<br />\n「港版國安法」制訂在即，將顛覆國家政權在內的4種行為列為罪行。7名市民今午(25日)到中聯辦請願，就中央訂立「港版國安法」遞交建議書，提出5項建議，包括在港設立維護國家安全執法局；法律實施後首3年在內地設立審判庭，之後再視具體情況在港設立審判庭；在港觸犯國家安全法的疑犯在內地受審，刑期在內地執行；國安法要有追溯期；及香港檢控機關及法官可在首3年在內地學習執行及實施國安法。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/bkn-20200525161245583-0525_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fbkn-20200525161245583-0525_00822_001.html&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3t%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=e6e00c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/bkn-20200525161245583-0525_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果有追溯期，請問應追溯到幾時? 1997抑或1949?</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"331bbd90239211a1643600f48c3ed7ee54d15f1a","tid":2034504,"uid":215634,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"舉腳贊成，我係外資一定走。"},{"pid":"b404bcb3746dd79795fe7ad89761dbc5dc5480a1","tid":2034504,"uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"331bbd90239211a1643600f48c3ed7ee54d15f1a","tid":2034504,"uid":215634,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"舉腳贊成，我係外資一定走。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:26:00.000Z","msg":"犯我中華者，雖遠必誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d490806a4b86003df11690b5d6dda0ebec2dee","tid":2034504,"uid":255637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:26:0